            <b style="font-size: 20px">Undeniable correlation between Education Attainment & Income Level for the general population</b>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md text-center">
            <b style="font-size: 20px">Tertiary Education offers people with the highest possibility of a high-paying job</b>
